node.title: Police appeal for information on missing Taupō woman
node.description: Police are investigating the disappearance of a woman in Taupō.
node.content:
["Police are investigating the disappearance of a woman in Taupō.", "", "
Missing Taupō woman Jan-Marie Burton Photo: Supplied / Police
", "Jan-Marie Burton has been reported missing by her family and was last seen yesterday at 4pm.", "In a statement, Taupō police said items of the woman's clothing have been located on Kinloch Beach, near the boat ramp on Kinloch Esplanade.", "They say her family and police are concerned for her wellbeing and anyone with information should dial 111."]
